==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Boatbill
<hw>Boat"bill`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A wading bird (<spn>Cancroma cochlearia</spn>) of the
tropical parts of South America. Its bill is somewhat like a boat with
the keel uppermost.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A perching bird of India, of the genus
<gen>Eurylaimus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Boat bug</ent>⟦br⟧
